import React from 'react'
import { Image } from 'react-native'
import {  View, FormControl, Stack, Input, Container } from 'native-base'

export default function Home() {
  return <View w="90%" maxWidth="300px" marginBottom={'250px'} >
      <FormControl>
        <Stack mx="4">
          <FormControl.Label fontWeight={'bold'}>Value A</FormControl.Label>
          <Input bg='primary.50' borderRadius={'10px'} />
          <FormControl.Label marginTop={'20px'} fontWeight={'bold'}>Value B</FormControl.Label>
          <Input bg='primary.50' borderRadius={'10px'} />
        </Stack>
        <Image source={'@expo/snack-static/react-native-logo.png'}/>
      </FormControl>
    </View>
}
